title: S15 Ep67: Omnipresent: Dark Force
itunes:title: Omnipresent: Dark Force
description:
Darkness Radio goes toe to toe with evil, Omnipresent: Dark Force with guest Lynn Monet

A single Mom with dreams of a better life, finds the house of her dreams....but we must remember, nightmares are dreams as well.

Lynn Monet faces the biggest challenge of her life and confronts an evil she never saw coming, an evil that tested her mind, body and spirit and shook her faith to the core. How do you deal with a force that is overwhelming, unrelenting and worst of all, omnipresent?
